highlights.text: SZA has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “Kill Bill” is the highest at #3.
“Believer” by Imagine Dragons has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 306 weeks straight.
“Shirt” by SZA is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 89 spots at #21.
“Kill Bill” by SZA is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #3.
